c: 20
v: 47
t: "Toysa isin kaal amaay:nanu diggah ku-Rabbi koo fan ruube namma farmoyta kinninok, toysa israa-iil xaylo nê luk ruubaay ken ma-digaalin, nummah nanu ku- Rabbik baxxaqqa itta asta koh luk nemceetek, firqawnaw Yallih digaalak nagaynan lem kay tirto kataate marak kay tirto kataata kaak ixxica"